<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Wmiellet – Personal Page</title>
  <style>
    /* Simple reset and basic styling */
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #222;
    }

    /* Navigation / Tab bar */
    .tabs {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .tabs a {
      display: inline-block;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .tabs a:hover {
      background-color: #1abc9c;
      color: white;
    }

    /* Active tab (optional – for the current page) */
    .tabs a.active {
      background-color: #1abc9c;
    }

    /* Main content */
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TAB BAR / NAVIGATION -->
<div class="tabs">
  <a href="/" class="active">Home</a>
  <a href="/tutorial.html">Tutorial</a>
  <!-- You can add more tabs later, e.g. Projects, Contact -->
</div>

<!-- PERSONAL PAGE CONTENT -->
<div class="container">
  <h1>Hi, I'm Wmiellet 👋</h1>
  <p>Welcome to my personal corner of the web.</p>
  <p>I’m a developer / researcher / hobbyist (edit this to fit you).</p>
  <p>Here’s a bit about me:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>💻 I love building web tools and tutorials.</li>
    <li>📚 Currently learning [your interest].</li>
    <li>🎯 Goal: share knowledge through clear guides.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Check out my <strong><a href="/tutorial.html">Tutorial page</a></strong> for step‑by‑step guides.</p>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 Wmiellet – Built with ☕ and GitHub Pages
</footer>

</body>
</html>
